*Declare a constant which contains your name.

REPORT Z_ABAP101_031.

*To declare a constant in ABAP containing my name,
*we can use the 'CONSTANTS' statement:

CONSTANTS lc_my_name TYPE string VALUE 'Adam'.

*This code defines a constant named 'lc_my_name' of type
*'STRING' with the value 'Adam', which contains my name.
